{"tid":993772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：馬杜羅無權中斷委內瑞拉與美國外交關係　危害美國使命者　美國會追究責任","createTime":"2019-01-24T07:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T12:00:02.000Z","uid":147314,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"00b961771696038b6992d1313fdf21af70f0ddaf","tid":993772,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蓬佩奧：馬杜羅無權中斷委內瑞拉與美國外交關係</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2019-01-24 HKT 14:28</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1439734_1_L_20190124142838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1439734_1_L_20190124142838.jpg&h=7d457560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉反對派領袖、國會議長瓜伊多自行宣布出任臨時總統，並獲美國政府承認，現任總統馬杜羅隨即決定，中斷與美國的外交關係，並要求美國駐當地外交人員在72小時內離境。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧說，美國不承認馬杜羅政權是委內瑞拉合法政府，因此不認為前總統馬杜羅有合法權力，中斷與美國的外交關係或宣布美國的外交人員是不受歡迎。蓬佩奧又說，美國會採取適當行動，對危害美國使命和美方人員安全的任何人士，追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n多個國家包括加拿大、巴西和哥倫比亞都跟隨美國，承認瓜伊多是委內瑞拉合法總統，不過，墨西哥、古巴等國支持馬杜羅，歐盟則呼籲委內瑞拉舉行總統選舉。"},{"pid":"c073e1ebd7403b67c80394de957e131634237cf5","tid":993772,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439734-20190124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439734-20190124.htm&d=%2Bga%2BB%2FGfR5Xrt1IO9jR1Lk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ae6218c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439734-20190124.htm&h=c157d423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439734-20190124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cac4b352f5d07711a9ec047b28e2632b72df5ccf","tid":993772,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />